largest of the seven emirates in the U.A.E.
   The agreement is aimed at providing in-flight food worldwide for
Moslem passengers, who are not supposed to eat pork. Moslems also
are supposed to eat meat or poultry only if slaughtered while
Koranic verses are being chanted.
   The Marriott Corp. is based in Bethesda, Md.
