<2ND_LINE>PM-Foam Heads,0196</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Giant Foam Rubber Heads of Archie and Veronica at Large</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SAN FRANCISCO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Betty, Jughead and Reggie are safe at home
in Riverdale, but Archie and Veronica have lost their foam rubber
heads, which presumably are loose somewhere in San Francisco.
   ``We were horrified. We can't feel very comfortable with
somebody running around with Veronica's head, doing God knows
what,'' David Silberkleit, vice president of marketing or Archie
