rubber heads of Archie Andrews and Veronica Lodge, worth an
estimated $2,000 each.
   The heads apparently disappeared from the St. Francis-Westin
Hotel in San Francisco about two weeks ago. They were in town for a
performance at an annual newspaper comic strip awards.
   Fortunately, there were two Archie heads and Betty is filling in
for Veronica at scheduled appearances.
   ``For once in Betty's life she has Archie all to herself,''
Silberkleit said.
